= Usage =
[https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/framework/tools/signtool-exe <code>signtool.exe</code>] can be used to <code>sign</code> and </code>Verify</code> applications.

Note, that the Windows website uses a lowercase <code>s</code> for <code>sign</code> but a capital <code>V</code> for the <code>Verify</code> subcommands.

Detailed installation and usage instructions for Authenticode, <code>signtool.exe</code> are [[undocumented]] in the {{project name long}} wiki. Using Authenticode is [[unspecific|unspecific to {{project name long}}]].

